features: SOOTHING BABY TOY Afrique Alligator WubbaNub is a stuffed animal and infant pacifier combined into one soft, soothing toy; packaged in a clear box for easy gift giving
SEWN-IN PACIFIER Latex-free, 100% silicone pacifier recommended for babies 0-6 months (babies without teeth); BPA, PVC and Phthalate free

EASY FOR BABY TO GRASP Adorable stuffed animal alligator with gorgeous green fabric and embroidered details, soft toy is 6-inches long; easy to hold, keep track of, and manipulate the pacifier, eliminates the need for pacifier cords or clips
MACHINE WASHABLE Wash in cold water in mesh laundry bag on gentle cycle, air dry; soft toy made to strict quality standards to meet or exceed US safety requirements
AFRIQUE BOUTIQUE A delightful baby shower gift, coordinate with soft toys from the Afrique Boutique collection, our modern safari themed family of toys that look great in any nursery
body.description: What is a WubbaNub? It's a combination stuffed animal and pacifier with durable one-piece construction. The soft toy animal makes it easy for baby to grasp and manipulate the pacifier, and is easier to keep track of than a soother on its own. Latex-free, 100% silicone pacifier recommended for babies 0-6 months (babies without teeth); pacifier is BPA, PVC and Phthalate free. Both functional and stylish, this WubbaNub is brought to you with an exclusive license with Mary Meyer. Look for more from our Afrique Boutique collection, mix and match with our Afrique lion, zebra, alligator, and elephant soft toys, rattles, teethers, and more.
